Wenger on Giroud: &quot;I have a huge respect for the man he is, for the way he loves our club. Even with all this speculation, he does his job.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger: &quot;Lacazette will play most of the time at centre forward. He played behind Giroud tonight on the left. He can play there as well.&quot;

Wenger on Mbappe: &ldquo;We haven&rsquo;t made any offer. I think he will stay, it looks like that. One more season. Maybe he has too much choice.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Wenger on if he&rsquo;s made a &pound;120m bid for Mbappe: &ldquo;That&rsquo;s not true. People have a big imagination. What we know now is Mbappe is over &pound;100m.&rdquo;
